nYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong><br><img src=\"http://img41.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/8vCuLic43xug26QzYkxLJsWT3jp935I58m3O0Elmdib5wWqHmhLe0jRjvZdP5yKvXEdSYDfnWLkYJCyns2u1R2RQ/640?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 298.75px;\"><br></strong><strong>食材：</strong>银耳2朵、西梅5个、莲子20颗、冰糖适量</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">西梅银耳味道酸甜，口感润滑，适合口味不同的女性。除了滋润身体以外也有提气凝神的功效。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">▼<strong>『 姜枣糖茶 』</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong><br><img src=\"http://img21.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/8vCuLic43xug26QzYkxLJsWT3jp935I58tnABlKOSKpVje5dXDjGW4jXCiclAGITNNear1JYbadBice77hojVd3cw/640?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"width: 200px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 132.3170731707317px;\"><br></strong><strong>食材：</strong>大枣6个、生姜1块、红糖1勺、水适量</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">功效非常好，尤其是在治疗痛经方面非常有效！</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">（图文来自网络，版权归原创作者所有，如侵权，请联系删除。谢谢。）</p>','2017-05-25 22:04:50',0,0,0,1),(41,'油性肌肤怎么办，护肤四个步骤让脸部清爽~','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>护肤步骤一：温和洁面</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">温和洁面，跟油污说再见。对于大多数的油性肌肤来说，能够做到温和并且彻底地清洁皮肤是很重要的。油脂污垢在毛孔堆积，假如没有得到深层的清洁，会让毛孔变大，形成毛孔粗大的问题。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">另外强调温和的原因是，脸部肌肤相对身体的其他皮肤来说是比较娇嫩的，假如过度过量地清洁，让肌肤的油脂分泌混乱，从而会让出油的情况加剧，得不偿失。另外还会因为过度的清洁而让皮肤松弛老化，毛孔变大。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>护肤步骤二：调节水油平衡</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img31.vccoo.com:808/refer.aspx?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/QwX1qG2zojQ0hBLXDjOTP7dF1nqJIalyhndGbaDv4ib5mhJW0CcDkt4Usa9xTtdvPzXCNlldE99gYTB7Ck83QQw/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 450.8px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">调节肌肤水油平衡，帮助收缩毛孔。清洁完皮肤之后，我们需要及时为肌肤补充水分，同时也起到二次清洁的效果。为了能够让补水缩毛孔二者兼备，可以事先把化妆水放到冰箱中冷藏。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">冷藏的化妆水倒在化妆面上，把它敷在t区和脸颊，敷脸五分钟。帮助肌肤补充水分，调节水油平衡，缓解肌肤的出油问题。另外也通过冷敷的方法帮助收缩毛孔.</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>护肤步骤三：适当补充油脂</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img11.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/QwX1qG2zojQ0hBLXDjOTP7dF1nqJIalygVfNLr6ZtekEkCoicImxoxnNEkqbenicStgq7Rm5iaOgib3rQ1cf3PFLlA/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 372.4px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">适当补充油脂，帮助控油修复。不要以为油性肌肤就要“滴油不沾”，其实适当地补充油脂能够起到锁水保湿的作用，而且还能够让毛孔，角质的代谢正常，修复扩张的毛孔。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">使用适量清爽控油型的乳液涂抹在容易出油的t区，然后轻轻地带过脸颊，不要反复揉搓，否则会让乳液中矽粉揉散，破坏控油效果。假如是衰老型毛孔肌肤，选择含有胜肽、神经酰胺或者胶原蛋白成分的面霜是非常适合的。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>护肤步骤四：做好夜间控油工作</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img41.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/QwX1qG2zojQ0hBLXDjOTP7dF1nqJIalyMcvmaGKK0J9XeY1fJl0Fh7jniccB3gdFeZicGbiaMNhfapZTd5MgSjWAg/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 396.2px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">控油工作除了白天要做，晚上也要做。因为晚间肌肤的油脂分泌会更加的旺盛，而夜间分泌的油脂要在第二天白天才浮现在脸上，因此想让第二天清爽美丽，在前一天晚上就要做好控油工作。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">（图文来自网络，版权归原创作者所有，如侵权，请联系删除。谢谢。）</p>','2017-05-25 11:35:54',2,0,0,1),(42,'有眼袋怎么化妆？轻松几个步骤学会淡化眼袋','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">大眼袋，说明眼睛水肿或是血液循环不畅，皮肤肯定比较干燥脆弱。小编建议可以用清爽型的眼胶加上隔离霜混合，用手指把两者调匀，轻轻地涂上眼袋处，这样就能轻易上妆了。<strong>大眼袋切忌闪光效果</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">眼袋处的皮肤比较脆弱嫩薄，如果在眼袋处还涂上有闪光效果的粉底，就会自曝其短了。另外，还要选择较轻易推开的粉底液。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img12.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/I3C6EYU995gBSia00G6WSOcqWLEH106JdibyR8rXZQYEicRJSXNQWZ5PO5xticicsfYCDk8mqIL3R6qBkOwcvblrl3g/640?\" style=\"width: 200px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 148.57142857142858px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>用深浅视觉效果来平复大眼袋</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">用浅色遮瑕膏在眼袋下轮廓的位置描上一条线，在眼袋处涂上深一号的遮瑕膏，在衔接处微微调匀，一次来模糊眼袋的界限，这样就能在视觉上平复大眼袋。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img13.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/I3C6EYU995gBSia00G6WSOcqWLEH106JdxwuHfaNFORFoTAncXSuPCqehLaEY4ea21Geua6nD71dKRfyoKa0JXg/640?\" style=\"width: 200px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 130.40540540540542px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">除了对大眼袋的遮盖，我们还可以通过强调眉毛和眼妆的效果，来提高别人对眉眼的注意力，从而达到弱化眼袋的效果。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>选择最保险的棕色系眼影</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">眼影的颜色要避免太过饱和的颜色，如蓝、紫、绿等，而棕色系的眼影，如古铜色、烟灰色、大地色等就比较适合了，如果选择有金属光泽的眼影，更能弱化眼袋。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>用抢眼的睫毛来扬长避短</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">睫毛一定要够抢眼，越长越好，因为他是眼部向外延伸的工具，越长的下睫毛，越能遮盖大眼袋，产生让眼袋往内缩的视觉效果。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img61.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/I3C6EYU995gBSia00G6WSOcqWLEH106Jdoznhibwyg3iaW2fgLteRnhCsbrbCcB1USwhISBWYlOSCztAQAvH6CbwA/640?\" style=\"width: 200px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 129.2929292929293px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>用上挑的眉弓提精神</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">大眼袋会让人有外眼角下垂的感觉，所以，注意绝对不能化下垂眉毛或一字眉，把眉弓尽量往上化，才能看起来精神百倍。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img21.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/I3C6EYU995gBSia00G6WSOcqWLEH106JddCtOZURNAWEe7SM5ZZk8Jc1sicsb5xEDoMKJRAvPAPRwnSNYmxN0l3g/640?\" style=\"width: 200px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 153.125px;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>用腮红</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">把腮红往上斜着打在鼻翼两侧，向太阳穴两处晕开，可以减弱眼袋的垂下感，也让脸色更加红润，添加好气色。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img13.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/I3C6EYU995gBSia00G6WSOcqWLEH106JdxAJzKUomFEcnPTx6QJPoYSryq26xWFvLgysJ0zz5eH0KzhywMhia3pA/640?\" style=\"width: 200px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 193.93939393939394px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">另外，<strong>需要切记的是</strong>，无论在办公室还是派对上，要尽量避免坐在灯光直射下来的地方，那会让大眼袋十分明显。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">（图文来自网络，版权归原创作者所有，如侵权，请联系删除。谢谢。）</p>','2017-05-25 11:34:32',1,0,0,1),(43,'为什么要尊重每个出门化妆的女生，因为。。。。','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>她为了见你可是花了血本啊~</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>因为化妆品都很贵！</strong><strong><br></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>这时候的她，不是她</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>是会呼吸的人民币</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img21.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_gif/0MckBzUZ9Tyo4sPib5mFf84KU2CoVSxibwpDQ3cYUaNX7hyEsliaicPeiaIUq1PLzYO6APyUnWdrmRdaEOmveXmg3sA/0?wx_fmt=gif\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 314.72px;\"></p><p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong><strong></strong></strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong><br></strong></p></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; font-style: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></strong></p>','2017-05-25 09:32:58',1,0,0,1),(44,'排毒可不是上厕所那么简单，5招清扫体内的毒素！','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">很多人都知道，我们每天上厕所是为了给身体排毒，流汗也是为了给身体排毒，但身体里的毒素可不止这么简单。一旦毒素堆积人就容易生病，那身体一旦有毒素会有什么症状呢？一起来了解一下吧。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img12.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/hHCgRL19ZjQvmib0w91luicp6h6q4s9TdLYC6enRCIozEic4cJCOSoPsTicsJ1tjibVupJD2Fj4pGcv905TMl7WV0ibg/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 344.2381786339755px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">人体内易出现的毒素</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">1</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>湿毒</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">湿是水的异常形态，由水转化而来。体内有湿毒的人，一般表现为舌苔白腻、恶心、不想吃饭、大便不成形等。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">湿毒主要是因脾气虚，不能化湿导致的。我们常吃的食物中，豆类最养脾，可以用各种豆子熬成粥喝；还可以用党参、白术炖肉吃，有不错的健脾除湿、升清降浊效果。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">2</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">水毒</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">阴毒中最严重的就是水毒，一般由肾功能衰弱引起。40岁以上的人应该注意，如果早上起来下眼皮、脚踝浮肿，很有可能就是水浊。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">想要驱逐水毒，首先要看医生，检查肾脏和心脏有无疾病，如果水毒是因肾功能不好导致的，而肾脏和心脏都没有病，那说明气血运行不好，需要多运动。饮食上可多吃一些除水湿的丝瓜、冬瓜等。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img13.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/hHCgRL19ZjQvmib0w91luicp6h6q4s9TdL2MbW74qtrMJgBfet20rUtKsAJ4gAEbnmqEnGhqia13PD39icJrCMw5nQ/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 343.18840579710144px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">3</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>痰毒</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">有的人早上起来不停吐痰，没完没了，这就说明有痰毒了。痰毒一般由饮食而来，或因肺功能不好导致。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">如果气管不好，痰多，可以喝二陈汤来治愈，一服药茯苓、法半夏、陈皮、甘草，用水煮了喝，喝上7天痰即可化。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">日常饮食上，萝卜是最好的化痰食物，可以买生萝卜加点香醋凉拌吃；另外还可以多吃冬瓜、无花果、紫菜、罗汉果等清热化痰之品。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">4</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>脂毒</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">有脂毒的人一般偏胖、脂肪较多。经常喝酒、吃肉、吃油炸食品，对肝脏伤害很大，易得脂肪肝等疾病。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">想清除脂毒，首先要降血脂，建议用山楂、荷叶煮水喝，可化痰降脂。平时应多吃洋葱等蔬菜；还可按揉小腿上的丰隆穴(位于外踝尖上8寸，条口穴外，距胫骨前缘二横指处)，可以消食导滞，减少脂肪。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img21.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/hHCgRL19ZjQvmib0w91luicp6h6q4s9TdLAwRwNZ7GkXfogcUsyvJgMYOLNNkbr2IU7qS6gmMXWEqHdgzo3NxkZg/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 339.36px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">5</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>气毒</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">气毒是存在肺里面的毒，中医认为“肺主气”、“肾主纳气”，有气毒的人往往肺肾功能不好，一般身上气味大，如有口臭、汗臭等。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">为了防止气毒，可以每天早起做深呼吸，即“呼吸吐纳”，把肺中的浊气排出来，保持体内空气的新鲜。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">6</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>瘀毒</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">瘀毒是指藏在血液里的毒，大多是从中年开始出现的，一般表现为舌下脉络发紫、容易健忘、皮肤干燥、胸闷憋气、脸色暗等。有瘀毒的人，可以用丹参或山楂泡水喝，有活血化瘀，清除血管垃圾之效。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">上面为大家介绍了身体阴毒的症状及排毒方法，肝脏是最主要的排毒工厂，因此，保护好我们的肝脏对排毒有很大作用，养肝护肝可以多吃新鲜蔬菜、多喝菊花茶。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img61.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/hHCgRL19ZjQvmib0w91luicp6h6q4s9TdL6uIzowhrUQw4eYR3TFclETibsmibeSWRUk8JT6LMostA33gbXQaR0a2w/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 336px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">日常如何清除体内毒素</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">1、多吃绿色食物助排便</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">深绿色蔬菜富含抗氧化剂、多种维生素、矿物质以及其他植物营养素，其抗炎作用可以令免疫系统保持活力。绿色蔬菜还富含膳食纤维，有助于促进排便，保证毒素的排出。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">所以，可以将菠菜、羽衣甘蓝、莴苣、甜菜等蔬菜，加少量酱汁拌成沙拉食用，也可将这些蔬菜加水榨成汁喝。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">专家指出，水果中同样含有丰富的膳食纤维，且维生素含量更高，因此，多吃水果会有类似的好处。比如，可用将香蕉、桃、梨、芒果、蓝莓等混合榨汁食用。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img61.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/hHCgRL19ZjQvmib0w91luicp6h6q4s9TdLD4KdxM6lKyl40Uof1gY5nRBmKTqGGLsKJdxQoBGC7jNquzNeW9Qlyw/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 358.4px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">2、少吃高能量食物促代谢</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">少吃糖、少吃加工食物，比如高糖的饼干、面包，或奶酪等，因为这些食物会阻碍身体各系统的工作速度，影响代谢。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">可以这样一点点做出改变：一次只吃一小块，然后再用其他更健康的食物来填肚子。比如，用芹菜拌鹰嘴豆、菠菜拌花生来代替奶酪等。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">不妨先尝试两个星期，看看你的身体到底会出现什么变化。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img11.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/hHCgRL19ZjQvmib0w91luicp6h6q4s9TdLtbbcYZURPicCOkq8gxBm34ozUBXHHngebkoiaT7xtysz1sgibeWEyzuqQ/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 351.8324607329843px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">3、多喝温柠檬水利排尿</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">人体60%~70%由水构成，水还可以帮助搬运体内的垃圾，其重要性不言而喻。每人每天应保证6~8杯水。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">对大部分健康人来说，判断你喝水够不够的标准之一就是：如果你每天小便的次数不足10次，那就再加点吧。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">此外，在水中加入半片柠檬或柠檬果汁，趁热喝，有利于消化系统和淋巴系统的正常工作，进而起到促进清除体内垃圾的作用。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">同时，柠檬水还可以帮助肝脏排毒，平衡内分泌；美国芝加哥洛约拉大学研究证明，其所含的柠檬酸盐有抑制肾结石形成的作用。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img12.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/hHCgRL19ZjQvmib0w91luicp6h6q4s9TdLJDod7Ju2N02xo1klT3iba2uBWeM7DI8JpG6WnuQ9zNBKj06GAHVFb3A/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 344.7111111111111px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">4、热水泡脚</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">脚是人体的第二心脏，热水泡脚能够使气血运行通畅，增加足部的血液流速和流量，增强新陈代谢。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">水温以40℃左右，温暖舒适为宜；时间控制在20~30分钟。特别是在夏天，这种方法的排汗排毒效果更好。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img12.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/hHCgRL19ZjQvmib0w91luicp6h6q4s9TdLu4657ajde5115NZSYJ9vicjtjzteVng7eRfWe9ejROJBGnico2tKdoEw/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 338.24px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">5、只吃八分饱有利消化</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">吃饭八分饱，二分留空余。换句话说，当你觉得胃里还没填满，但对食物的热情已经下降时，就要停下来了。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">这种吃饭方式不仅有利于肠胃健康，还可以让身体像加足润滑油的机器，运行无碍。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">此外，这样的习惯可以抵消掉一部分因吃垃圾食品而导致的不利影响，为你偶尔的饮食放纵上了一道保险。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">（图文来自网络，版权归原创作者所有，如侵权，请联系删除。谢谢。）</p>','2017-05-25 09:35:51',3,0,0,1),(45,'这样洗脸会毁容的！怪不得皮肤越来越差了！','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img41.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iaBhvGUicq0hVdnoBeIicvQwJFiaxPPhJiayLbByhAyS9B44YfG1uiaibYrcvZ8jGHf0zibTrXLj211WiaoLCPcLRbgic8zQ/0?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 590.8px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">既然是洁面就要泡沫在面部充分停留，才能深层次的洁净肌肤或者说让洁面乳的功效充分发挥，很多姑娘为此小小得意。其实就算是油性肤质，多在出油部位加强按摩30-60秒钟，超过一分钟以上的时间，会让肌肤过干，反而会导致肌肤代偿性出油，形成干燥型油性肌肤。</p><p><strong style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">过度使用冷热水</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img61.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/iaBhvGUicq0hVdnoBeIicvQwJFiaxPPhJiayLicn6mzP49pYrGb0icYS6VP8M9krQbOPqjEUbqUjuPVic5NqNKHLR1uLQA/0?\" style=\"width: 200px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 255.85585585585585px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">用凉水洗脸感觉很清爽，但感官的舒适却对肌肤并无好处，过凉或过热都会对肌肤造成一定的刺激，尤其是针对油性肌肤来说，会大大刺激油脂的分泌。一般来说用不超过四十度的温水洗脸为最好，如果想要收缩毛孔的话，可以在温水洁面后用冷水进行收缩。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>湿毛巾擦干面部</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img31.vccoo.com:808/refer.aspx?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz/5avcj00HmqPHICD3Gu5uoEcuatYl3WePGnjolwZIPOOYUbRPB7wuJOUfLpEIvJjKCjULmibibjtbIlGW3vibH7sgA/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 643.937360178971px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">反正都是自己一个人在用，毛巾的干湿就顺其自然，或者直接用湿毛巾擦干面部的水分。实际上毛巾具有良好的吸湿和储水性能，所以久湿不干的毛巾容易滋生各种微生物，用湿毛巾洁面，肌肤上的油脂、灰尘、水中的杂质、空气中的细菌都会沉积在毛巾上。特别是油脂分泌比较旺盛的女性，毛巾更容易受污染，造成皮肤受伤，毛孔堵塞。因此毛巾必须时常保持清洁干燥，用手洁面之后再用干毛巾擦拭，既快又卫生。</p><p><strong style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">过分洁面</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">很多姑娘受不了面部分泌的大量油脂，拼命的洗脸以求解脱。但这种做法是非常不可取的，过分的洁面会破坏皮肤表层的保护膜，让角质层变得脆弱不堪，肌肤就会变得越来越敏感，更多的肌肤问题会纠缠着你。正确的洁面一天不要超过三次，早晚各一次为最好。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">（图文来自网络，版权归原创作者所有，如侵权，请联系删除。谢谢。）</p>','2017-05-25 09:29:45',1,0,0,1),(46,'比阿胶还养人！五月初，女人最该吃的就是它！','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">时令果蔬最养人，符合自然生长的规律，味道鲜美，营养价值高，是养生的理想食物。5月多吃这9种时令果蔬，你已经吃过哪几种了呢？<br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img12.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lapIXIae9ziaSHxrvlM1NUF99UeRIDwbGOB6gfcURl1mPLj2QFvmibMLWhiaBV8nhxBn76u8GHzHdxPsUIY9kSRqQ/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 560px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">芹菜</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">芹菜含有丰富的铁元素和膳食纤维，补血效果不错，还可以促进人体脂肪分解，是减肥的理想食物。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img21.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lapIXIae9zgGTAgp77UfYo6X6Uvx4KibLSc3nH1BHOJblF4wwapIZePicP3ialvlG0BQSHZic4R9SX4QM4yqra4vibA/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 813.1914893617021px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">推荐吃法：&nbsp; 热炒和凉拌均可，芹菜叶维生素C比茎多，最好连芹菜叶一起吃，芹菜脆爽，口感很好。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img11.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/HNQAJXEiarLpiaJQvbslPnhPmHcD85cBpib1ic6CtfDDPKFboibLGKcPick4Dp6nickTc7FyB9KrxHL2TB684YqgwbdXw/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 617.75px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">选购技巧：&nbsp; 芹菜梗20厘米—30厘米为宜，短而粗壮为佳。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img21.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lapIXIae9zgGTAgp77UfYo6X6Uvx4KibLIFibFEcP1MbrdMEazvf38cO07KicOlqrApMhHJA4r2zQuRTJnMaqxt1g/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 560px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">莴笋</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">莴笋里的莴苣素可以和钙一起平复兴奋的神经，有安神的效果，也能增进食欲，加上含钾量高，有助于减少心房压力。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img12.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/lapIXIae9zgGTAgp77UfYo6X6Uvx4KibLkzCInSxnpNyTQkLD0LNERrKkswdCXMiaOw0qAokkUpIBpsDaq5prN5g/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 392px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">推荐吃法：&nbsp;&nbsp;炒或凉拌均可，盐会破坏莴笋营养，少盐为宜，推荐清炒莴笋、莴笋炒木耳、莴笋炒猪肉，味道鲜美又有营养。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img31.vccoo.com:808/refer.aspx?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lapI