ily: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">推荐吃法：&nbsp;&nbsp;可煮可炒，炒的时间要短，汤羹非常鲜美。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img41.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lapIXIae9zgGTAgp77UfYo6X6Uvx4KibLA1ETD7bXw4Xv25uGhIS61mbvqCiaWbej5uGcHBAW2Jh8pjAjgAtkp9w/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 515.2px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">选购技巧：&nbsp; 叶尖萎蔫的不要买；老的鸡毛菜柄也比较长，选择菜柄15厘米以内的会更嫩。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img12.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lapIXIae9zgGTAgp77UfYo6X6Uvx4KibL7sAB17EoibChibPBRcCaWFY3vcSDcrRYdDkCoAV2Z63LEzWiagPUfD7PA/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 638.4397163120567px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">心</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\