ragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">选购技巧：&nbsp; 叶片为绿色带光泽、包裹紧密、分量偏重的卷心菜更好。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">豆</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">豌豆鲜绿圆润，富含维生素C和维生素A原，具有防癌抗癌的功效，还能润泽皮肤，很多人都喜欢。<br></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img12.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/lapIXIae9zgGTAgp77UfYo6X6Uvx4KibLnOlib44bhper4icibhhM0dMrMGbnL4y9cqhO0YLSibu1whD5VVGlGg61iaQ/640?\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 773.4751773049645px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">推荐吃法：&nbsp; 可煮可炒，清炒豌豆、虾仁炒豌豆、肉末炒豌豆味道都不错。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://img13.vccoo.com/refer.php?url=http://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/HNQAJXEiarLpiaJQvbslPnhPmHcD85cBpibMPLoaVSN8c9RlfDzVEY4wqkUzZVCA8iat