100%; height: 840px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">（图文来自网络，版权归原创作者所有，如侵权，请联系删除。谢谢。）</p>','2017-06-01 05:51:57',5,0,1,1),(47,NULL,NULL,'2017-05-28 01:16:28',0,0,0,1),(48,'枸杞泡酒的不同泡法，赶紧收藏！','<p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">药酒以其是将药物以其适用范围广，便于服用，吸收迅速，见效快疗效高、便于储存等几大特点被人们重视;</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">因酒本身也是一种<strong>药物</strong>，有畅通血脉、散瘀活血、祛风散寒、消冷积、医胃寒、健脾胃、提精 神和引药上行、助药之力等功效，所以，酒和药加在一起，可以增强药效，浸泡于酒中，使药中的有效成分溶于酒中，目的是利用酒的辛温行散之性，以活络通经。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>枸杞泡酒</strong>具有<strong>益气、补肝、明目、安神、润肺、抗肿瘤、延缓衰老等作用</strong>，是百姓家中常用泡酒食材，但是我们的泡酒方法是否正确？不同的配方有不同的比例。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>下面我们就根据不同的枸杞泡酒配方来看看枸杞泡酒的比例如何吧！</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>一、清肝明目，疏风散热，肝虚白内障，迎风流泪酒又叫疏风明目酒</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://read.html5.qq.com/image?src=forum&amp;q=5&amp;r=0&amp;imgflag=7&amp;imageUrl=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/AxJIyhp6e0k5AgTe57LNaQibOBa8Ix2nYxG5gHBGT0ibKFcAOslQbnB9wQCFLl6INCxAemVmtuqnnVEOp9mjc3pw/0\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 350px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"></p><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">配方：枸杞50克，黄酒2000毫升。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">制法：将枸杞浸入黄酒中，密封贮存、4个月即可。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">服法：每次服30～50毫升，每日服2次，饭后服用。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>二、补脑益肾、补齐益精杞圆酒</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://read.html5.qq.com/image?src=forum&amp;q=5&amp;r=0&amp;imgflag=7&amp;imageUrl=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/AxJIyhp6e0k5AgTe57LNaQibOBa8Ix2nYUPjCGOM22hRaPB9aYoK6WABBAh0SZcJrjv0JCicVibvdRFYHbGdCjMCA/0\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 350px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"></p><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">配方：枸杞、龙眼肉各50克，好白酒500克。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">制法：将上药浸入酒中，封固，7天后即可饮用。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">服法：每次饮1小杯，每日1-2次。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>三、养心安神、补血益精、强身健体枸杞地黄酒</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://read.html5.qq.com/image?src=forum&amp;q=5&amp;r=0&amp;imgflag=7&amp;imageUrl=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/AxJIyhp6e0k5AgTe57LNaQibOBa8Ix2nY3cJHA6cJyqgZhsrb6icf40q9iaTTia1YN1CIqFJIaeI5hr5aMuFIUKpMg/0\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 350px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"></p><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">配方：枸杞10克，肉苁蓉20克，茯苓20克，熟地黄20克，山茱萸20克，牛膝20克，远志20克，五加皮20克，石菖蒲20克，地骨皮20克，白酒1000毫升。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">做法：将前10味切碎，装入布袋，置容器中，加入白酒，密封浸泡，14日后去渣即成。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">服法：每日早、晚各服1次，每服15毫升。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>四、补精养髓、益肾健脾、润燥枸杞参白酒</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 