ding: 0px;\">服法：每日早、晚各服1次，每服10～15毫升。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><strong>五、补虚益精，祛寒助阳枸杞虫草酒</strong></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"http://read.html5.qq.com/image?src=forum&amp;q=5&amp;r=0&amp;imgflag=7&amp;imageUrl=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/AxJIyhp6e0k5AgTe57LNaQibOBa8Ix2nYJvs0ib1stB2SwTcF4zG6IicibpYOP49pZHt7aZMzAiaszDnss9ukjcHkPA/0\" style=\"width: 560px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; display: block; margin: auto; max-width: 100%; height: 350px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"></p><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">配方：冬虫夏草10克，枸杞40克，白酒500毫升。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang 