ragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"></p><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">配方：肉苁蓉鲜干片100克，锁阳50克，枸杞50克，白酒4斤。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">制作方法：将上述3味药浸于白酒中，密封，置阴凉处，2周后即可。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><li style=\"margin: 0px 0px 24px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\">服法：每日1次，睡前温服1小杯。</p><p style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px;\"></p></li><p><img src=\"http://read.html5.qq.com/image?src=forum&amp;q=5&amp;r=0&amp;imgflag=7&amp;imageUrl=https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/AxJIyhp6e0k0OLjnF7bQXHxWEia9kSiaicJ4pFPG2vU81jiasibtYGuagmTGmb5SnVyvkaTCiaeJ3tQFvj7wPshtL6rA/0\" style=\"width: 200px; background-color: transparent; color: transparent; margin: auto; display: block; max-width: 100%; font-family: \'PingFang SC\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'WenQuanYi Micro Hei\', \'Helvetica Neue\', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 18px; text-align: justify; height: 200px;\"><br style=\"margin-bottom: 24px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: \'PingFa